NEWS for the R Package Luminescence

Changes in version 0.6.3 (9th September 2016):

  Bugfixes and changes:

         • ‘analyse_baSAR()’

             • Fix problem that causes a function crash if an XLS-file
               was provided as input for the grain selection

         • ‘analyse_pIRIRSequence()’

             • Account for minor layout problem while plotting the
               combined growth curve.

         • ‘plot_AbanicoPlot()’

             • The relative and absolute standard deviation had been
               mixed up in in the summary; fixed.

